cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper deals with visual attribute classification, which is a common task in computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses multi-task and curriculum learning, which are topics related to machine learning. Hence, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely sub-categories. The paper uses publicly available datasets, which suggests that it may fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as well.
